{"tid":576272,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星際特工","createTime":"2018-02-28T18:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T20:28:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2298eb6aeb995c38a38c15cc2c2ff2c16490f3f3","tid":576272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=iclPFWTIwMZQmcEcnueLSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cc321757\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=iclPFWTIwMZQmcEcnueLSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5a0d5ace\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a8/Valerian_and_the_City_of_a_Thousand_Planets_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa8%2FValerian_and_the_City_of_a_Thousand_Planets_Poster.jpg&h=2f80be6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事設定於28世紀的未來，敘述瓦雷諾（丹恩&middot;德翰 飾演）和蘿琳娜（卡拉&middot;迪樂芬妮 飾演）是由人類特派的負責維護整個宇宙秩序的星際旅行特工。瓦雷諾不僅是蘿娜琳的搭檔，還是她的公開追求者。可是由於他的眾多緋聞與女主角傳統價值觀格格不入，導致他的追求之路重挫。受指揮官-艾倫（克萊夫&middot;歐文 飾演）的委派，瓦雷諾和蘿娜琳前往令人心曠神怡的星際城市阿爾法執行一項任務。這是一座欣欣向榮正在不斷擴張的城市，居住來自宇宙各個角落的物種。三千萬的星際居民正在協同努力，積聚他們的智慧和才能讓這個城市變得更加美好..<br />\n<br />\n2 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=iclPFWTIwMZQmcEcnueLSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=29e35a5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=iclPFWTIwMZQmcEcnueLSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9fda20e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463f963fa7f077c1fdc3548dad19835b0ab45f35","tid":576272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d30e5fd8356fc6384ca77fa65a613b6c3050ed","tid":576272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae772fa8b273584019229ac8e339979e71a041d","tid":576272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181a0012cf4cd11dad206f65c93a321c8fbba331","tid":576272,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T20:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}